---
import '../styles/global.css';
---

<html lang="tr">
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
		<meta name="generator" content={Astro.generator} />
		<title>KDK Portal | Kayıt ve Denetim Platformu</title>
		<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
		<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
		<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600&family=Outfit:wght@600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
		<meta name="description" content="KDK Portal - Modern Kayıt ve Denetim Yönetim Sistemi. Sertifikasyon ve denetim süreçlerinizi dijitalleştirin.">
	</head>
	<body class="min-h-screen">
		<!-- Navigation -->
		<nav class="fixed top-0 w-full z-50 glass border-b-0">
			<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 h-20 flex items-center justify-between">
				<div class="flex items-center gap-2">
					<div class="w-10 h-10 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary to-secondary rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
						<span class="text-white font-bold text-xl">K</span>
					</div>
					<span class="text-2xl font-display font-bold bg-clip-text text-transparent bg-gradient-to-r from-white to-slate-400">
						KDK Portal
					</span>
				</div>
				
				<div class="hidden md:flex items-center gap-8">
					<a href="#" class="nav-link">Anasayfa</a>
					<a href="#" class="nav-link">Sertifikalar</a>
					<a href="#" class="nav-link">Denetimler</a>
					<a href="#" class="nav-link">Kurumsal</a>
				</div>

				<button class="btn-primary">Giriş Yap</button>
			</div>
		</nav>

		<!-- Hero Section -->
		<section class="relative pt-32 pb-20 overflow-hidden">
			<div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
				<img src="/hero-bg.png" alt="Background" class="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-30 scale-105" />
				<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-surface/20 via-surface to-surface"></div>
			</div>

			<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 relative z-10">
				<div class="max-w-3xl animate-fade-in">
					<div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-primary/10 border border-primary/20 text-primary text-sm font-medium mb-6">
						<span class="relative flex h-2 w-2">
							<span class="animate-ping absolute inline-flex h-full w-full rounded-full bg-primary opacity-75"></span>
							<span class="relative inline-flex rounded-full h-2 w-2 bg-primary"></span>
						</span>
						Yeni Nesil Denetim Sistemi
					</div>
					
					<h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl mb-6 leading-[1.1]">
						Geleceğin <span class="text-primary">Kayıt ve Denetim</span> Standartları
					</h1>
					
					<p class="text-xl text-slate-400 mb-10 max-w-2xl leading-relaxed">
						KDK Portal ile tüm sertifikasyon, denetim ve kayıt süreçlerinizi tek bir platformdan yönetin. 
						Veri odaklı yaklaşımımızla güvenliği ve verimliliği en üst seviyeye taşıyın.
					</p>

					<div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
						<button class="btn-primary px-8">Hemen Başlayın</button>
						<button class="px-8 py-3 rounded-full border border-border-main hover:bg-white/5 transition-colors font-semibold">
							Bilgi Alın
						</button>
					</div>
				</div>

				<!-- Stats Grid -->
				<div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-6 mt-20 animate-fade-in delay-200">
					{[
						{ label: 'Aktif Şirket', value: '1.2k+' },
						{ label: 'Sertifika', value: '5.4k+' },
						{ label: 'Başarılı Denetim', value: '12k+' },
						{ label: 'Yıllık Artış', value: '%40' }
					].map(stat => (
						<div class="card">
							<div class="text-3xl font-display font-bold text-white mb-1">{stat.value}</div>
							<div class="text-slate-400 text-sm">{stat.label}</div>
						</div>
					))}
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- Features -->
		<section class="py-20">
			<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
				<div class="text-center mb-16 animate-fade-in delay-300">
					<h2 class="text-4xl mb-4">Neden KDK Portal?</h2>
					<p class="text-slate-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Modern işletmeler için tasarlanmış, esnek ve güçlü özelliklerle dolu bir ekosistem.</p>
				</div>

				<div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
					<div class="card group">
						<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-primary/20 transition-colors text-primary text-2xl">
							🛡️
						</div>
						<h3 class="text-xl mb-3">Güçlü Güvenlik</h3>
						<p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
							Tüm verileriniz en üst düzey şifreleme yöntemleri ile korunur ve periyodik olarak yedeklenir.
						</p>
					</div>

					<div class="card group">
						<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-secondary/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-secondary/20 transition-colors text-secondary text-2xl">
							⚡
						</div>
						<h3 class="text-xl mb-3">Hızlı İşlem</h3>
						<p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
							Optimize edilmiş altyapımız sayesinde en karmaşık raporlamaları bile saniyeler içinde tamamlayın.
						</p>
					</div>

					<div class="card group">
						<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-accent/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-accent/20 transition-colors text-accent text-2xl">
							📊
						</div>
						<h3 class="text-xl mb-3">Gelişmiş Analiz</h3>
						<p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
							Yapay zeka destekli analiz araçlarımızla denetim trendlerini takip edin ve riskleri önceden belirleyin.
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<footer class="py-12 border-t border-border-main">
			<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-6 text-slate-500 text-sm">
				<div>© 2026 KDK Portal. Tüm hakları saklıdır.</div>
				<div class="flex gap-8">
					<a href="#" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Gizlilik Politikası</a>
					<a href="#" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Kullanım Şartları</a>
					<a href="#" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Destek</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</footer>
	</body>
</html>
